honestly, it's just plants

Some people are skeptical - we get it. But it happens to be true: the only ingredients we use are organic plants. No colors, flavor enhancers, preservatives or fillers. No added sugars or artificial sweeteners. Just the worlds best produce, with the water taken out so that the nutrients stay in.

Theres never been an easier way to reach your recommended five servings of daily fruits and vegetables. All the nutrients and flavor from real organic produce, and none of the hassle.

free nutrition coaching

We know that new habits are easier to stick to if youve got a supportive crew behind you. Thats why we offer every member free nutrition coaching courses with our Registered Dietitians.

healthy habits, healthy planet

Almost half of the worlds fresh fruits and vegetables are thrown away uneaten. Our flash-freeze, slow-dry process cuts waste by putting produce on standby until youre ready to enjoy it.
